{"tid":656362,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【贏《鐵達尼號》】《復仇者3》香港史上最高票房第3位","createTime":"2018-05-07T07:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-07T13:35:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c3dfc8e77d67dc2b450be8c52e04f223c1d69beb","tid":656362,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20180507/s00009/3ee38340b463d30191f5dca6fb48024b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20180507%2Fs00009%2F3ee38340b463d30191f5dca6fb48024b.jpg&h=e1fc7765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMarvel電影《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》4月25日在香港上映，上畫12日累積票房衝破$118,637,066港元 （資料由香港影業協會及香港戲院商會屬下機構香港票房有限公司提供），擊敗《鐵達尼號》（$115,306,690港元），成爲香港史上最高票房第3位。下一步將會挑戰亞軍《復仇者聯盟2：奧創紀元》的$133,061,397港元成績，相信應該無難度，但要刷新冠軍《阿凡達》的$178,029,440港元紀錄，則可能有點難度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1525678499799&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180507\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1525678499799%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180507&d=PipUh5SrMdnZYIP%2FzYps9DA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=779d59ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1525678499799%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180507&h=ddc7f2b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1525678499799&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180507</a>"},{"pid":"95c29c5f3bdc84b46bf4bacdb4464db80bb7402e","tid":656362,"uid":61282,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"反而想知鐵達尼號如果計埋通脹會係幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756047968ea020355d4d6c4a65e57e3104684a52","tid":656362,"uid":75765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"遲下再上畫咪得"},{"pid":"b4f413cf878597b124c3873d25657047f1ecaf29","tid"